Program: Discovery
Title: Pain of Torture
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/w3cswdkk
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 19 Feb 2018
Does knowing that someone is inflicting pain on you deliberately make the pain worse? Professor Irene Tracey meets survivors of torture and examines the dark side of pain. Producer: Geraldine Fitzgerald (Photo: A woman mourns during the funeral procession of Abdulrassul Hujairi. Credit: Joseph Eid/AFP) Show less